PrecisAppointment of Nancy Goodman, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration Appeal Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of seven years; and designation of Nancy Goodman as Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, effective September 1, 1994.
